<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Lower Mount Royal</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-xl">17th Avenue borders the north of the community and is a favourite destination for people
                looking for entertainment and shopping. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">A mix of well known retail shops and unique owner-operated shops, from Blame Betty to
                Purr, shoppers will find a satisfying amount of shops to browse around and buy different accessories and
                clothing. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">17th Avenue also offers a large array of dining choices, from the quick bites of Tubby Dog
                and Kim Anh Vietnamese Subs to the restaurants of Fiore Cantina Italiana to Boston Pizza.</p>

            <p class="par-lg">River Park and Altadore Park are located in the south end of Mount Royal and are an
                excellent outdoor area for picnics, fires and afternoon walks. The upper portion of River Park is an
                off-leash dog park, making it ideal for dog owners.</p>

        </div>
